9922187322699931682.Text: Tholer Saryoni told me that the Third Corner of the House of Troubles is Molag Bal. I must find the statue of Molag Bal in Bal Ur and recite Vivec's "Four Corners." Bal Ur is north of Suran, but I will need to levitate over the mountains to get there easily.

1922446231583025364.Text: I made the Pilgrimage to Bal Ur and read a passage from the Four Corners of the House of Troubles.

1936126244197972048.Text: Temple: Molag Bal of the House of Troubles
